---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Get help" description="Free, confidential mental-health support and crisis resources. If you are struggling, reaching out is the strongest move you can make.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pt-12 pb-16">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Get help</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-moss-deep">You don't have to manage this alone</h1>
    <div class="prose-mr mt-6">
      <p>If your mood is low and it's affecting your daily life, the most effective step isn't a supplement — it's talking to someone who can help. A doctor or therapist can look at the whole picture in a way no website can. Reaching out is a sign of strength, not weakness.</p>
      <p>If you are in immediate danger or thinking about harming yourself, please contact your local emergency number right now.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
      <div class="bg-card border border-mist rounded-lg p-5">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-moss-deep">United States</h2>
        <p class="text-ink-soft mt-1">Call or text <strong>988</strong> — the Suicide &amp; Crisis Lifeline, available 24/7. You can also chat at <a href="https://988lifeline.org" class="text-saffron-deep underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">988lifeline.org</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-card border border-mist rounded-lg p-5">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-moss-deep">United Kingdom &amp; Ireland</h2>
        <p class="text-ink-soft mt-1">Call <strong>Samaritans on 116 123</strong>, free, 24/7. Or text <strong>SHOUT to 85258</strong>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-card border border-mist rounded-lg p-5">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-moss-deep">Elsewhere</h2>
        <p class="text-ink-soft mt-1">Find a helpline in your country through the <a href="https://findahelpline.com" class="text-saffron-deep underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Find A Helpline</a> directory, or contact your doctor or local health service.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>
</Base>
